      "citation_id": "[CITATION_5]",
      "span_text": "Although PARP protein has previously been shown to localize to centrosomes and chromosomes during cell division and in the interphase  , to our best knowledge this is the first morphological demonstration of increased poly(ADP-ribose) polymerase activity in mitotic cells."
